data.name: petalPerfectDescription.Text
data.value: A classic arrangement of ravishing red roses, paired together with pretty-in-pink petals and sprays of lush foliage. Treat them to the Petal Perfect experience on their special day, to put the widest smile on their face, or simply just because - with the perfect mini bouquet for those cherished moments.

data.name: annelieseDescription.Text
data.value: Made worthy for a princess - with soft pink gerberas, roses, and carnations, and frills of white aster. Our Anneliese flower bouquet the sweetest gesture of tender, loving care to truly light up her day.

data.name: hotromanceDescription.Text
data.value: A bouquet of red roses accompanied by white statice. A bouquet wrapped to perfection and suitable for any occasions as red roses simply symbolizes your passion, true love and desire while leaving the white statice to portray your utmost sincerity. This is the go-to gift that expresses your love and intentions without having to say a word.
